<p>I'm moving to Florida before it disappears under the ocean.</p>
<p><a href="http://geochange.er.usgs.gov/pub/poster/sealevel.html"><img src="https://halcanary.org/images/2006-03-03-flooded-10m.png" alt="[Red shows areas along the Gulf Coast and East Coast of the United States that would be flooded by a 10-meter rise in sea level. Population figures for 1996 (U.S. Bureau of the Census, unpublished data, 1998) indicate that a 10-meter rise in sea level would flood approximately 25 percent of the Nation's population.]" height="239" width="593" /></a></p>
<p>Seriously. When my lease is up, I'm out of here.</p>

